{"tid":240368,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一定有聽過阿媽叫你食完飯要飲水幫助消化","createTime":"2017-05-12T11:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T11:17:58.000Z","uid":79792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2314450b7799312f0bc56ad029c4953b5cd5a5","tid":240368,"uid":79792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"但其實係咪真係要飲呢 上網搵左D資料<br />\n<br />\n(大公報)<br />\n飯後飲水：飯後馬上飲水會稀釋胃液，削弱了胃液的消化能力，容易引發胃腸道疾病。如果飯後喝的是汽水那對身體就更為不宜了，汽水產生的二氧化碳容易增加胃內壓，導致急性胃擴張<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"http://health.takungpao.com.hk/ys/q/2013/1219/2116436.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhealth.takungpao.com.hk%2Fys%2Fq%2F2013%2F1219%2F2116436.html&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=942de39b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://health.takungpao.com.hk/ys/q/2013/1219/2116436.html</a><br />\n<br />\n(每日頭條)<br />\n其實無論飯前還是飯後喝水對胃的消化其實沒有太大影響，不必擔心喝水會稀釋胃液，也很少導致消化不良的發生<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/qg3l6y.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2Fqg3l6y.html&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=72a792d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/qg3l6y.html</a><br />\n<br />\n究竟飯後飲水對身體有無影響 有無BIO專家可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}